msgid "Check DB Consistency"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/release_notes/release_notes/upgrade_44.rst:85
msgid ""
"After the upgrade is completed, you should run the command ``onedb fsck``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/release_notes/release_notes/upgrade_44.rst:87
msgid ""
"First, move the 4.4 backup file created by the upgrade command to a safe "
"place."
msgstr ""

